<refentry xml:id="function.odbc-primarykeys" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>odbc_primarykeys</refname>
  <refpurpose>Obtém as chaves primárias de uma tabela</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>
 <refsect1 role="description">
  &reftitle.description;
  <methodsynopsis>
   <type class="union"><type>Odbc\Result</type><type>false</type></type><methodname>odbc_primarykeys</methodname>
   <methodparam><type>Odbc\Connection</type><parameter>odbc</parameter></methodparam>
   <methodparam><type class="union"><type>string</type><type>null</type></type><parameter>catalog</parameter></methodparam>
   <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>schema</parameter></methodparam>
   <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>table</parameter></methodparam>
  </methodsynopsis>
  <para>
   Retorna um objeto de resultado que pode ser usado para buscar os nomes das colunas
   que compõem a chave primária de uma tabela.
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="parameters">
  &reftitle.parameters;
  <para>
   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
     <term><parameter>odbc</parameter></term>
     <listitem>
      &odbc.connection.id;
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
     <term><parameter>catalog</parameter></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       &odbc.parameter.catalog;
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
     <term><parameter>schema</parameter></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       &odbc.parameter.schema;
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
     <term><parameter>table</parameter></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="returnvalues">
  &reftitle.returnvalues;
  <para>
   &odbc.result.object-return-falseforfailure;
  </para>
  <para>
   O conjunto de resultados possui as seguintes colunas:
   <itemizedlist>
    <listitem><simpara><literal>TABLE_CAT</literal></simpara></listitem>
    <listitem><simpara><literal>TABLE_SCHEM</literal></simpara></listitem>
    <listitem><simpara><literal>TABLE_NAME</literal></simpara></listitem>
    <listitem><simpara><literal>COLUMN_NAME</literal></simpara></listitem>
    <listitem><simpara><literal>KEY_SEQ</literal></simpara></listitem>
    <listitem><simpara><literal>PK_NAME</literal></simpara></listitem>
   </itemizedlist>
   &odbc.result.driver-specific;
  </para>
  <simpara>
   O conjunto de resultados é ordenado por <literal>TABLE_CAT</literal>, <literal>TABLE_SCHEM</literal>,
   <literal>TABLE_NAME</literal> e <literal>KEY_SEQ</literal>.
  </simpara>
 </refsect1>

